\pard{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf3\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-720\li720\f0\fs19 If a character has STUN (or END) boosted through an Adjustment Power, as long as his STUN (or END) total remains equal to or greater than his normal full STUN (or END), he gets no benefi t to that Characteristic from Post-Segment 12 Recoveries or from normal Recoveries taken in a Phase (but see below). \b\par
