\pard{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf3\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-720\li720\b0 However, in some cases, characters will gain points of an expendable ability from an Adjustment Power that has a lengthy fade rate (such as \ldblquote points fade at the rate of 5 per Hour\rdblquote  or the like). In that situation, if a character uses some or all of the gained points, with the GM\rquote s permission he may use his REC to regain them during the duration of the Adjustment eff ect. \f1\fs20\par
