\pard{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf3\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-720\li720\b0 If a Drain or Transfer is used on the eff ect (like a change environement or supression field) but not the character who created it, the Adjustment Power reduces only the eff ect, not the character\rquote s power. If a Transfer is used on an eff ect, the character using it gains points from the use of Transfer as per normal.\fs20\par
